lead_paragraph: Striker Abel Hernandez will miss Uruguay's World Cup qualifiers against Ecuador and Chile because of a groin injury, his club Hull City said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Hull Striker Hernandez Ruled Out of Uruguay Qualifiers
headline.main: Hull Striker Hernandez Ruled Out of Uruguay Qualifiers
